title: New Antminer T21 190T 3610W 380V-415V Algorithm SHA-256 Bitmain Mining BTC Bitcoin Miner with Power Cord
body_html:
Brand: OEMGMINER

Features:

  • High computing power and power efficiency: The ANTMINER T21 has a computing power of up to 190TH/s and an excellent power efficiency of 19 J/TH, making it suitable for efficient mining.
  • Applicable cryptocurrency types: This miner is dedicated to mining cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin (BTC), Bitcoin Cash (BCH), and Bitcoin SV (BSV), meeting diverse mining needs.
  • Network connection method: Uses RJ45 Ethernet connection method, facilitating stable connection with the network to ensure smooth mining operations.
  • Environmental adaptability: Normal operation within the operating temperature range of 0~45°C and supports non-condensing humidity of 10~90%, adapting to different environmental conditions for mining needs.
  • Good transportation packaging: Equipped with high-quality transportation packaging with dimensions of 570*316*430mm and a net weight of 17kg, facilitating quick and easy transportation and handling processes.

Binding: Personal Computers

EAN: 0762730041080
